{"tid":2232495,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【Staycation】逾20人酒店屈蛇開生日派對被趕   港女：太嚴苛!!!","createTime":"2020-10-06T11:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T09:04:09.000Z","uid":66271,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e7bdfb14398ed8527f1b76abf52d1e2b68aac6de","tid":2232495,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/10/20201006_CR_%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F10%2F20201006_CR_%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597-1.jpg&h=687abe0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/10/20201006_CR_%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F10%2F20201006_CR_%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597-2.jpg&h=e6f5b9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港第三波疫情有舒緩跡象，確診數字近日漸見回落，不少港人趁長假期訂酒店房「Staycation」或開Party。為確保公眾衛生，不少酒店會限制房間內的人數聚集。近日一名港女在本港一酒店租住一間房間舉辦生日派對，邀請逾20人到場，被酒店方要求客人離開，讓她大感掃興，更在社交網站抱怨酒店太嚴苛，惹來網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n該港女在社交網站撰文指自己第一次籌辦派對，本打算在酒店房間內舉行盛大的生日派對，讓好友有一個「豪華的享受」。然而酒店以限聚令為由，拒絕港女帶多位朋友進入房間。原定於晚上七時半開始的派對，在未開始前港女和朋友已被要求離開，最後眾人移師到另一間酒店慶生，令她的派對變得「美中不足」。<br />\n<br />\n該名港女辯稱，從新聞得知酒店不屬限聚令所規限，酒店進行防疫措施只屬建議，認為涉事酒店的做法有點嚴苛。她得知被投訴後，希望先與朋友大合照後再收拾物資、重訂另一間酒店，惟酒店職員每隔一小段時間就按門鈴提示他們要立刻離開，並表明會一直在門外等候直至人群離去，令他們感到十分不滿。她強調自己和朋友們一直保持低音量及地方整潔，對酒店的處理方法非常失望，形容是次經歷是他們的罕有體驗，又表示「有錢都唔會再光顧」。<br />\n<br />\n港女表示，她與朋友曾經在其他方開派對，「好多年」都未遇過這種情況。惟有網民認為港女的行為十分過份，並指出酒店平常容許多於限定人數聚集房間內，只是「隻眼開隻眼閉」，現時港女違反規定反而怪責別人，並不合理"},{"pid":"4d0a16ae5553225aa65e21770d1bbd6977459798","tid":2232495,"uid":103759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"20p大混戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b24dff0557e9fc8daafef57ebb24ab81d44186","tid":2232495,"uid":112645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"del咗post唔係咩"},{"pid":"3283f623c514c598a093a23b6b255de91f25f5c0","tid":2232495,"uid":124,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"好心香港人既唔好咁肉酸啦<br />\n<br />\n屈蛇開party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cefa95b3e23bb2cf35a17f4eccfc102c96fd72","tid":2232495,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e25a0af80d53ba690cc3c09a301ff632279561","tid":2232495,"uid":281439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7bdfb14398ed8527f1b76abf52d1e2b68aac6de","tid":2232495,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/10/20201006_CR_%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F10%2F20201006_CR_%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597-1.jpg&h=687abe0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/10/20201006_CR_%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F10%2F20201006_CR_%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597-2.jpg&h=e6f5b9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港第三波疫情有舒緩跡象，確診數字近日漸見回落，不少港人趁長假期訂酒店房「Staycation」或開Party。為確保